OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fbright evening with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee clear spells, and perhaps the odd
OL,9,Fmist or fog patch developing later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FDry and bright with the
OL,12,Fbest chance of some bright or hazy
OL,13,Fsunny spells during the afternoon.
OL,14,FWarm, particularly in the west.
