OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly dry with very warm sunshine
OL,7,FThursday, chance of the odd shower.
OL,8,FCloudier later Thursday and Friday
OL,9,Fmorning with the risk of a few
OL,10,Fshowers. Rain spreading east on
OL,11,FSaturday.
